teams.description:
The Global Poverty Initiative goals are as follows: 

1.  End Global Poverty and hunger;  
2.  Preserve the environment; 
3.  Empower women. The program will provide food production skills and training in self-reliance through gifts of seeds, livestock and training in environmentally sound agriculture. Education in sustainable food practices will make women equal partners in ending poverty and hunger. We have global partners for self-help projects and awareness campaigns within the United States and abroad.
